'''Tromin unigarments''' were a type of form-fitting unigarment. Twin sisters [[Ann Gella/Legends|Ann]] and [[Tann Gella/Legends|Tann Gella]] were forced to wear these garments during their enslavement by [[Dug/Legends|Dug]] podracer [[Sebulba/Legends|Sebulba]].

